"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[12]&nbsp;D.L. Donoho, “Denoising by Soft Thresholding,” <em>IEEE Transactions on Information Theory</em>, vol. 41, no. 3, pp. 613-627, 1995. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/18.382009\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Denoising+by+Soft+Thresholding%2C%E2%80%9D+IEEE+Trans.+On+Inf+Theory&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/382009\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[13]&nbsp;P.M. Agante, and J.P. Marques de sa, “ECG Noise Filtering Using Wavelets with Soft Thresholding Methods,” <em>Computers in Cardiology</em>, vol. 26, pp. 535-538, 1999. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/CIC.1999.826026\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=ECG+noise+filtering+using+Wavelets+with+Soft+thresholding+methods&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/826026\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[14]&nbsp;Marteen Jansen, <em>Noise Reduction by Wavelet Thresholding</em>, Springer, 1<sup>st</sup> ed., 2001. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/978-1-4613-0145-5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Noise+reduction+by+Wavelet+Thresholding&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: