n+on+the+Compact+Ability+of+Asphalt+Mixtures+Utilizing+Locking+Point&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\" previewlistener=\"true\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://ascelibrary.org/doi/10.1061/%28ASCE%29MT.1943-5533.0003609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\" previewlistener=\"true\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[15]&nbsp;Waleed Zeiada et al., “Review of the Superpave Performance Grading System and Recent Developments in the Performance-Based Test Methods for Asphalt Binder Characterization,”&nbsp;<em>Construction and Building Materials</em>, vol. 319, 2022. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/j.conbuildmat.2021.126063\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\" previewlistener=\"true\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Review+of+the+Superpave+performance+grading+system+and+recent+developments+in+the+performance-based+test+methods+for+asphalt+binder+characterization.&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\" previewlistener=\"true\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0950061821037958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\" previewlistener=\"true\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[16]&nbsp;Consultant Committee Report, “<em>Remedy of Variations in Asphalt Concrete Mixture</em>,” Ministry of Housing and Construction, Final Report, 1993.&nbsp;</p>', '2024-07-11', '2024-08-01', '2024-08-22', '2024-09-28', '../my-app/public/upload/DST/volume-3/issue-3/DST-V3I3P101.pdf', '2025-09-25 09:48:28', '2025-09-25 11:19:26', 'published');
