 Economic Forum, Shaping the Future of Artificial Intelligence: A Multi-Stakeholder Approach, 2019. [Online]. Available: </span>https://example.com/future-ai-multi-<span style=\"color: rgb(13, 13, 13);\"> Stakeholder. </span>Haut du formulaire</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">[12] E. Xie, “Artificial Intelligence is Watching China’s Students, but How Well can it Really See?,” </span><em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">South China Morning Post</em><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">, 2020. </span>[online]. Available: <span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3027349/artificial-intelligence-watching-chinas-students-how-well-can.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">[13]&nbsp;Z. Zhang,. Intelligence: A modern look. Intelligence, </span><em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Higher Education Press</em><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">, Beijing, China, vol. 46, pp. 1-4, 2014. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/.intell.2014.06.007\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">[14]&nbsp;</span>Slimi Zouhaier,<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"> “</span>The Impact of Artificial Intelligence on Higher Education: An Empirical Study,”<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">&nbsp;</span><em>European Journal of Educational Sciences</em>, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 17-33.., 2023. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=The+Impact+of+Artificial+Intelligence+on+Higher+Education%3A+An+Empirical+Study&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.ceeol.com/search/article-detail?id=1111750\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">[15]&nbsp;Shengquan Yu, and Yu Lu., Bridging Human and Machine Future Education with Intelligence, </span><em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">Springer</em><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\">, 2022,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(13, 13, 13);\">.</span></p><p><br></p>', '2024-04-11', '2024-05-12', '2024-06-01', '2024-06-12', '..\\my-app\\public\\upload\\LLL\\volume-2\\issue-2\\LLL-V2I2P102.pdf', '2025-09-25 12:53:55', '2025-09-25 12:53:55', 'unpublished');
