of+the+English+language+training+need+analysis+for+engineering+students+in+India%2C%E2%80%9D+English+Language+Teaching%2C+vol.+8%2C+no.+2%2C+pp.+116%E2%80%93125%2C+2015.&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://eric.ed.gov/?id=EJ1075200\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[13]&nbsp;S.P. &nbsp;Dhanavel, <em>English and Soft Skills</em>, Orient Black Swan, Hyderabad, 2010. </p><p>[14]&nbsp;NASSCOM, <em>Strategic Review: The IT-BPM Sector in India 2019: Decoding Digital</em>, India, 2019.</p><p>[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=NASSCOM%2C+Strategic+Review%3A+The+IT-BPM+Sector+in+India%2C+National+Association+of+Software+and+Services+Companies&amp;btnG=#d=gs_cit&amp;t=1750066744446&amp;u=%2Fscholar%3Fq%3Dinfo%3A5YU_OAU7GmMJ%3Ascholar.google.com%2F%26output%3Dcite%26scirp%3D0%26hl%3Den\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>]</p><p>[15]&nbsp;Asif Aziz et al., “A Needs Analysis of Communicative Needs of Engineering Students in AJ&amp;K,” <em>International Journal of Special Education</em>, vol. 37, no. 3, pp. 1807-1818, 2022. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=A.+Aziz%2C+et+al.%2C+%E2%80%9CA+Needs+Analysis+of+Communicative+Needs+of+Engineering+Students+in+AJ%26K%2C%E2%80%9D+International+Journal+of+Special+Education%2C&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>]</p><p>[16]&nbsp;Uzma Nisar, and Aejaz Mohammed Sheikh, “Challenges of Teaching English Communication Skills in NIT Srinagar,” <em>Language in India</em>, vol. 25, no. 1, pp. 70–79, 2025. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Challenges+of+Teaching+English+Communication+Skills+in+NIT+Srinagar%2C%E2%8