ql-align-justify\">[5] SN Maitra, “Application of Lagrange’s Multiplier: Some Optimisation Problems Related to Physics,” <em>International Journal of Research Publications and Reviews</em>, vol. 4, no. 8, pp. 2675-2682, 2023.<span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: black;\">[</span><a href=\"https://www.ijrpr.com/archive.php?volume=4&amp;issue=8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a><span style=\"color: black;\">]</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[6] R. Tyrrell Rockafellar, “Lagrange’s Multipliers and Optimality,” <em>SIAM Review, Society of Industrial and Applied Mathematics</em>, vol. 35, no. 2, pp. 30-56, 1993.<span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: black;\">[</span><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1137/1035044\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a><span style=\"color: black;\">] [</span><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Lagrange%E2%80%99s+Multipliers+and+Optimality&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a><span style=\"color: black;\">] [</span><a href=\"https://epubs.siam.org/doi/10.1137/1035044\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a><span style=\"color: black;\">]</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[7] Phil Lucht, “The Method of Lagrange’s Multipliers,” Remrock Digital Technology, Salt Lake City, 2016.<span style=\"color: black;\"> </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: black;\">[</span><a href=\"about:blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a><span style=\"color: black;\">]</span></p><p><br></p>', '2025-01-16', '2025-02-12', '2025-03-02', '2025-03-18', '../my-app/public/upload/MS/